ai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868800/extras/d818edcd7e1d1a2c87bb41e8dcee0ade.avif?t=1715369992\" width=610 height=142 /></span><br>By completing orders in the story mode, increase your skill level and earn to develop your workshop. Each order has specific requirements that we must meet in order to satisfy our clients.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868800/extras/3e232283a7baa6281120c4112f10173b.poster.avif?t=1715369992\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868800/extras/3e232283a7baa6281120c4112f10173b.webm?t=1715369992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868800/extras/3e232283a7baa6281120c4112f10173b.mp4?t=1715369992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868800/extras/a23b3e4363e9deee4c1ef148814328da.avif?t=1715369992\" width=610 height=142 /></span><br>The design mode will allow you to freely personalize shoes with access to all tools, save designs and export them to formats that are helpful for real customization.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868800/extras/08a7cf2dbc45225e0261488b430d1731.poster.avif?t=1715369992\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868800/extras/08a7cf2dbc45225e0261488b430d1731.webm?t=1715369992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868800/extras/08a7cf2dbc45225e0261488b430d1731.mp4?t=1715369992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Do 